  "slug": "music-notification",
  "title": "Music Notification",
  "description": "Configure visual notifications when music is played in-game",
  "body": "# Music Notification\n\nAdds a toast notification when music is played in the game with the track’s name, author, and album name.\n\n### **Require**: [Cloth Config API](https://modrinth.com/mod/cloth-config)  \n\nIf you have any issues, feel free to open a issue in [GitHub](https://github.com/KosmoMoustache/MusicNotification/issues)\n\n# 📷 In game screenshots\n<div>\n    <table>\n        <tr>\n            <td align=\"middle\">\n                <img alt=\"\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/KosmoMoustache/MusicNotification/next/.github/assets/style/legacy_toast_album.webp\"/>\n                <figcaption align=\"middle\">\"Show album name\": true</figcaption>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td align=\"middle\">\n                <img alt=\"\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/KosmoMoustache/MusicNotification/next/.github/assets/toasts.png\"/>\n                <figcaption align=\"middle\">Different Toast configuration</figcaption>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td align=\"middle\">\n                <img alt=\"\" src=\"https://github.com/KosmoMoustache/MusicNotification/raw/1.21.8/img/modded1.png\"/>\n                <figcaption align=\"middle\">Works with modded content (<a href=\"\"https://modrinth.com/mod/more-music-discs>More Music Discs</a>)</figcaption>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n       <tr>\n            <td align=\"middle\">\n                <img alt=\"\" src=\"https://github.com/KosmoMoustache/MusicNotification/raw/next/.github/assets/jukebox_home_tab.webp\"/>\n                <figcaption align=\"middle\">Play any music anywhere at anytime using the Jukebox Menu</figcaption>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </table>\n</div>\n\n# 🎀 Notification Style\n\n<div>\n    <table>\n        <tr>\n            <td align=\"middle\">\n                <img alt=\"\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/KosmoMoustache/MusicNotification/next/.github/assets/style/legacy_toast.webp\"/>\n                <figcaption align=\"middle\">Normal Toast</figcaption>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td align=\"middle\">\n                <img alt=\"\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/KosmoMoustache/MusicNotification/next/.github/assets/style/action_bar.webp\"/>\n                <figcaption align=\"middle\">Action Bar</figcaption>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td align=\"middle\">\n                <img alt=\"\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/KosmoMoustache/MusicNotification/next/.github/assets/style/compact.webp\"/>\n                <figcaption align=\"middle\">Compact</figcaption>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </table>\n</div>\n\n# ⚙ Settings\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/KosmoMoustache/MusicNotification/next/.github/assets/config.png\">\n\n\n# Video Preview\nhttps://youtu.be/HK2swFtPanA\n\n# Customization\nTo add support for custom music or customize existing tracks you need to add a file named `musics.json` inside custom resource pack under the namespace `musicnotification`.\n\nJSON Schema can be found here: [DOCS.md](https://github.com/KosmoMoustache/MusicNotification/blob/next-stonecutter/DOCS.md)\nIf you have any question, feel free to fill an issue.\n\n# Contributor\nDiscs icon are made by [carotteatomique](https://github.com/carotteatomique)  \nMod icon was made by [akairoo](https://dribbble.com/akairoo)  \nSimplified Chinese translation by [Chiloven945](https://github.com/Chiloven945)",
